Subtitle.seed(
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:46:00Z", "end_time"=>1.71096503734589, "id"=>529, "start_time"=>0.258569002151489, "text"=>"What is machine learning?", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:46:07Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:56:23Z", "end_time"=>101.261451721191, "id"=>548, "start_time"=>96.3559265136719, "text"=>"Here's a slightly more recent definition by Tom Mitchell, who's a friend over at Carnegie Mellon.", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:56:42Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:50:07Z", "end_time"=>38.6824989318848, "id"=>536, "start_time"=>33.0373611450195, "text"=>"Samuel's claim to fame was that back in the 1950s, he wrote a checkers playing program.", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:50:26Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:46:13Z", "end_time"=>7.48647499084473, "id"=>530, "start_time"=>1.73698902130127, "text"=>"In this video, we will try to define what it is and also try to get a sense of when you want to use machine learning.", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:47:06Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:00:50Z", "end_time"=>136.0, "id"=>555, "start_time"=>133.049713134766, "text"=>"The task T would be the task of playing checkers,", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:01:38Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:10:34Z", "end_time"=>209.227645874023, "id"=>568, "start_time"=>206.093292236328, "text"=>"and this experience E,", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:10:51Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:56:46Z", "end_time"=>105.000648498535, "id"=>549, "start_time"=>101.827110290527, "text"=>"So Tom defines machine learning by saying that -", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:57:18Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:47:09Z", "end_time"=>15.1345081329346, "id"=>531, "start_time"=>8.4000940322876, "text"=>"Even among machine learning&nbsp;practitioners, there isn't a well-accepted definition of what is and what isn't machine learning.", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:47:55Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:08:51Z", "end_time"=>201.523077160221, "id"=>566, "start_time"=>195.62196216285, "text"=>"So, hopefully you got that this is the right answer - classifying emails is the task T.", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:09:37Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:48:36Z", "end_time"=>24.9685059714346, "id"=>534, "start_time"=>20.3643843029432, "text"=>"Here's a definition of \"what is machine learning\" due to Arthur Samuel.", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:49:31Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:07:46Z", "end_time"=>188.929656982422, "id"=>564, "start_time"=>181.827255249023, "text"=>"In a few seconds, the video will pause, and when it does so, you can use your mouse to select one of these four radio buttons,", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:08:38Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:05:54Z", "end_time"=>169.619018554688, "id"=>560, "start_time"=>163.062576293945, "text"=>"an email program like this you might click this spam button to report some email as spam but not other emails.", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:06:45Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:57:21Z", "end_time"=>107.665614401647, "id"=>550, "start_time"=>105.192886352539, "text"=>"the well-posed learning problem is defined as follows.", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:58:12Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:01:24Z", "end_time"=>143.367462158203, "id"=>556, "start_time"=>136.531707763672, "text"=>"and the performance measure P would be the probability that it wins the next game of checkers against some opponent.", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:02:30Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:47:16Z", "end_time"=>20.2674785934629, "id"=>532, "start_time"=>15.5831810318174, "text"=>"Let me show you a couple of examples of the ways that people have tried to define it.", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:49:12Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:51:10Z", "end_time"=>49.804, "id"=>538, "start_time"=>46.2227668762207, "text"=>"What he did was he had the program play tens of thousands of games against itself,", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:52:18Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:57:54Z", "end_time"=>115.093580095781, "id"=>551, "start_time"=>108.19685920955, "text"=>"He says, a computer program is said to learn from experience E with respect to some task T and some performance measure P,", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:58:47Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:51:21Z", "end_time"=>56.5637092590332, "id"=>539, "start_time"=>50.157, "text"=>"and by what sorts of board positions tended to lead to wins, and what sort of board positions tended to be to losses,", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:52:43Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:51:28Z", "end_time"=>62.8639689351723, "id"=>540, "start_time"=>56.9135513305664, "text"=>"the checkers playing program learned over time what are good board positions, and what are bad board positions", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:53:10Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:08:27Z", "end_time"=>193.855224609375, "id"=>565, "start_time"=>189.184555053711, "text"=>"to let me know which of these four you think is the right answer to this question.", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:08:50Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:51:42Z", "end_time"=>67.6317977905273, "id"=>541, "start_time"=>63.3272857666016, "text"=>"and eventually learned to play checkers better than Arthur Samuel himself was able to.", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:53:35Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:58:56Z", "end_time"=>120.211, "id"=>552, "start_time"=>115.236, "text"=>"if its performance on T, as measured by P, improves with experience E.", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:59:26Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:06:50Z", "end_time"=>178.096969604492, "id"=>562, "start_time"=>169.860488891602, "text"=>"And, based on which emails you mark as spam, say your email program learns better how to filter spam email.", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:07:32Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:53:37Z", "end_time"=>73.809, "id"=>542, "start_time"=>68.3877487182617, "text"=>"This was a remarkable result. Arthur Samuel himself turned out not to be a very good checkers player", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:54:07Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:53:43Z", "end_time"=>79.1652679443359, "id"=>543, "start_time"=>74.3436813354492, "text"=>"but because the computer has the patience to play tens of thousands of games against itself", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:54:29Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:53:48Z", "end_time"=>82.3054275512695, "id"=>544, "start_time"=>79.4015655517578, "text"=>"-- no human has the patience to play that many games --", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:54:41Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:03:57Z", "end_time"=>152.045548636763, "id"=>557, "start_time"=>144.577317435591, "text"=>"Throughout these videos, besides me trying to teach you stuff, I'll ask you a question to make sure you understand the content.", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:04:37Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:59:29Z", "end_time"=>123.913772583008, "id"=>553, "start_time"=>120.450012207031, "text"=>"I actually think he came up with this definition just to make it rhyme.", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:00:01Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:54:46Z", "end_time"=>87.6553933039727, "id"=>545, "start_time"=>82.6971084302126, "text"=>"By doing this a computer was able to get so much checkers playing experience", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:55:31Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:54:50Z", "end_time"=>91.9068603515625, "id"=>546, "start_time"=>87.6669158935547, "text"=>"that it eventually became a better player than Arthur Samuel himself.", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:55:52Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:04:50Z", "end_time"=>156.962280273438, "id"=>558, "start_time"=>152.150970458984, "text"=>"On top is the definition of machine learning, by Tom Mitchell --", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:05:21Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:55:56Z", "end_time"=>96.1495056152344, "id"=>547, "start_time"=>92.9566497802734, "text"=>"This is a somewhat informal definition, and an older one.", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:56:19Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:07:33Z", "end_time"=>181.373748779297, "id"=>563, "start_time"=>178.806427001953, "text"=>"What is the task T in this setting?", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:07:44Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:00:07Z", "end_time"=>132.415191650391, "id"=>554, "start_time"=>124.289527893066, "text"=>"For the checkers-playing example, the experience E would be the experience of having the program play tens of thousands of games against itself.", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:01:20Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:05:22Z", "end_time"=>162.663177490234, "id"=>559, "start_time"=>157.661117553711, "text"=>"Let's say your email program watches which emails you do or do not flag as spam, so", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:05:47Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:11:35Z", "end_time"=>221.978284295119, "id"=>570, "start_time"=>216.570920403518, "text"=>"and the fraction of emails correctly classified; that might be your performance measure P.", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:12:41Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:09:48Z", "end_time"=>205.679260253906, "id"=>567, "start_time"=>202.261184692383, "text"=>"This definition defines a task T and a performance measure P,", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:10:34Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:13:08Z", "end_time"=>234.91996311497, "id"=>572, "start_time"=>222.878733866924, "text"=>"and so, our task performance - our system's performance on the task T on the performance measure P will improve after the experience E.", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:14:36Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:10:54Z", "end_time"=>216.347610473633, "id"=>569, "start_time"=>210.0107421875, "text"=>"and so watching you label emails as spam or not spam, this would be the experience E,", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:12:24Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:14:51Z", "end_time"=>238.973281860352, "id"=>573, "start_time"=>235.354583740234, "text"=>"In this class, I hope to teach you about the various types of learning algorithms.", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:15:10Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:49:36Z", "end_time"=>31.8289834189444, "id"=>535, "start_time"=>24.9685059714346, "text"=>"He defined machine learning as the field of study that gives computers the ability to learn without being explicitly programmed.", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:50:04Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T06:50:29Z", "end_time"=>45.6690673828125, "id"=>537, "start_time"=>38.781, "text"=>"And the amazing thing about this checkers playing program was that Arthur Samuel himself wasn't a good checkers player.", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:17:03Z", "video_id"=>2, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:25:27Z", "end_time"=>11.004, "id"=>582, "start_time"=>5.1907190209077, "text"=>"DRG coming from the loser bracket, he has to win a best of 3 -", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:25:56Z", "video_id"=>21, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:26:04Z", "end_time"=>16.994, "id"=>583, "start_time"=>11.13, "text"=>"if he does not win two out of the first three games, then MarineKing has won and he is our champion -&nbsp;", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:26:52Z", "video_id"=>21, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:26:53Z", "end_time"=>23.5783013768485, "id"=>584, "start_time"=>17.1693013768485, "text"=>"and if he does, it turns into a best of 7, and of course, $10,000 on the line,", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:27:56Z", "video_id"=>21, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:27:39Z", "end_time"=>26.76, "id"=>585, "start_time"=>23.741, "text"=>"as well as top seed at Columbus pool play.", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:27:54Z", "video_id"=>21, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:28:47Z", "end_time"=>4.899, "id"=>586, "start_time"=>0.697, "text"=>"Thank you - please, thank you very much.", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:29:34Z", "video_id"=>20, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:30:21Z", "end_time"=>19.412, "id"=>588, "start_time"=>12.283, "text"=>"thank you so much for this very warm welcome, it is a great honor to be here at the Hankuk University of Foreign Studies -", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:31:10Z", "video_id"=>20, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:31:17Z", "end_time"=>25.797, "id"=>589, "start_time"=>19.714, "text"=>"[cheering]", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:31:34Z", "video_id"=>20, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:29:40Z", "end_time"=>11.981, "id"=>587, "start_time"=>6.293, "text"=>"To President Park, faculty, staff and students,", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:32:33Z", "video_id"=>20, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:31:40Z", "end_time"=>34.04, "id"=>590, "start_time"=>26.192, "text"=>"I want to thank Dr. Park for, a few moments ago, making me an honorary alumni of this university.", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:32:34Z", "video_id"=>20, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:32:40Z", "end_time"=>47.438, "id"=>591, "start_time"=>39.869, "text"=>"Now I know that this school has one of the world's finest foreign language programs, which means that your English is much better than my Korean.", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:33:09Z", "video_id"=>20, "voice"=>0},
  {"created_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:33:18Z", "end_time"=>nil, "id"=>592, "start_time"=>50.667, "text"=>"All I can say is - kam-sa-ham-mi-da. [cheers]", "updated_at"=>"2012-03-28T07:34:09Z", "video_id"=>20, "voice"=>0}
)

